{"title":"杜甫草堂","authors":["董耀章"],"dates":[{"year":1988,"month":10,"day":3}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"杜甫草堂"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"·董耀章·"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"穿过幽深的竹林，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我鼓荡湿润的风，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"绕过五彩花径，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"合着喷香的诗韵。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"怀着无限虔诚，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"前来拜谒诗圣，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"虽说茅屋早被秋风所破，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"但心里仍系着天下神经。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"岁月悠悠，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"留下草编的圆顶，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"几根柱子，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"擎着永恒的精英，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"亭子里储满千种情怀，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"喧哗着激荡着亮节高风。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"做人要像青竹一样挺拔"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"作诗应充满理智的激情"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我在大千世界昼夜跋涉，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是谁给了我常青的生命？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只要笔管里注满人民的热血，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"诗就会与人民共振！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}